<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
        varaiyātu vantu oḻukun talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattu niṉṟu kēṭpa nerunal illattu nikaḻntatu ituveṉat talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatu</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the heroine to the confidante, saying ’That which happened yesterday at the house was this’, as the hero who behaves, having come without a marriage [proposal], stands at the outer fence, listening.. </p>
         </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink113">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi neṉṉa</l>
<l>lōṅkutirai veṇmaṇa luṭaikkun tuṟaivaṟ</l>
<l>kūrār peṇṭeṉa moḻipa veṉṉai</l>
<l>yatukēṭ ṭaṉṉā yeṉṟaṉa ḷaṉṉai</l>
<l>paipaya vemmai yeṉṟaṉeṉ yāṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen! Yesterday,</l>
<l>The townspeople said, ‘[She is] the girl</l>
<l>To the man from the ghat upon which high waves break the white sand’.</l>
<l>Having heard that, mother said, ‘You are like that?’</l>
<l>Slowly/carefully, I said, ‘[He is] our Lord’.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
